    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it has been such a joy to own. It's in solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks and drives great without the brand-new price tag. It handles beautifully and is just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll fall in love with it just like I did!",
