    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip M-differential, ensuring precise power delivery. The chassis has been proactively maintained, including documented rear subframe reinforcement to address floor pan fatigue. Suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and high-speed stability these M-cars are renowned for. Recent preventative maintenance includes a valve lash adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with a driver-focused vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain are in excellent synchronized order.",
