    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2019 Lexus RX 350 finished in a timeless Obsidian Black over a Parchment leather interior. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and has been maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small, shallow scuff on the lower rear bumper consistent with careful use. The 18-inch alloy wheels are in great shape, showing only very light curb rash on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary. The leather seats are soft and free of any rips or heavy staining, with only light compression on the driver's bolster. All features are fully operational, including the power moonroof, heated and ventilated front seats, and the intuitive infotainment system with a crisp backup camera. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly and delivers power effortlessly through the 8-speed automatic transmission. All scheduled maintenance is up to date, including a recent synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection. The tires have roughly 60% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This Lexus offers a perfect blend of luxury and longevity, ready for many more miles of comfortable travel.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
